high_descs: Turn around and walk to the closest short side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the salt shaker.
Turn left and veer left to the shelves in the corner.
Put the salt shaker on the second to bottom shelf.
Turn around and walk to the furthest short side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the salt shaker on the counter.
Walk ahead and right, back to the shelves.
Put the salt shaker on the shelf to the right of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the shelf then turn left and walk until the white counter by the door is on your left and then turn to face it.
Pick up the salt shaker that's by the yellow handled knife.
Turn left and make it so you are standing facing the brown shelf in front of you looking at the wall behind it not the window.
Put the salt shaker on the second shelf to the left by the edge.
Turn left and walk to the white table in front of you then turn left and walk until the table to the right of you ends then turn right take a step and turn right so you are facing the white island.
Pick up the salt shaker that is in front of you.
Walk back to where you put the first salt shaker.
Put the salt shaker to the right of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit against the wall, then turn left again and walk to the closest end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the salt shaker that is closest to you off of the kitchen island.
Turn left and walk over to the wooden shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Place the salt shaker on the middle of the left side of the middle shelf.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then turn left again and walk over to far side of the kitchen island where the second salt shaker is.
Pick up the salt shaker off of the edge of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk back to the wooden shelving unit.
Place the salt shaker on the middle shelf just to the right of the salt shaker that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers the middle shelf of a wooden shelving unit.
